title: Big Papi 5-CD Christmas Pack Vol II Sinatra Neil Diamond Tony Be
description:
This is 5 CD's of Christmas Vocal genre.  Vocal is where the main focus is on the singer due to their amazing talent of singing in itself.  Most modern pop music has very little to do with vocal skills.

I hope you enjoy this mix of oldie, older, and newer.

- Big Papi
